{"parse":{"title":"compliments","pageid":206313,"redirects":[],"wikitext":"==English==\n\n===Pronunciation===\n* {{IPA|en|/ˈkɑmplɪmənts/|a=GA}}\n* {{IPA|en|/ˈkɒmplɪmənts/|a=RP}}\n* {{audio|en|en-us-compliments.ogg|a=US}}\n* {{hmp|en|complements}}\n* {{hyph|en|com|pli|ments}}\n\n===Noun===\n{{head|en|noun form}}\n\n# {{plural of|en|compliment}}\n# Good wishes.\n#: {{ux|en|Please accept this 2011 calendar with our '''compliments'''.}}\n\n====Usage notes====\n* In the sense of good wishes, one is often said to {{m|en|pay}} or {{m|en|present}} one's compliments to somebody.\n\n====Derived terms====\n* {{l|en|with compliments}}\n\n===Verb===\n{{head|en|verb form}}\n\n# {{infl of|en|compliment||s-verb-form}}\n\n==Catalan==\n\n===Pronunciation===\n* {{ca-IPA}}\n\n===Noun===\n{{head|ca|noun form}}\n\n# {{plural of|ca|compliment}}\n\n==French==\n\n===Pronunciation===\n* {{audio|fr|LL-Q150 (fra)-0x010C-compliments.wav}}\n* {{audio|fr|LL-Q150 (fra)-DenisdeShawi-compliments.wav|a=<<Canada>> (<<Shawinigan>>)}}\n\n===Noun===\n{{head|fr|noun form|g=m}}\n\n# {{plural of|fr|compliment}}"}}